review_blob: This is a great beer if you are in the mood for something light, sweet, and wheaty.  Its a good beer for connoisseur newbies.
This beer is better than no beer, but its definitely not good beer.  It looks, tastes, and smells like dirty water.
does "ice" mean "watered down"?  because this beer doesnt taste like anything more than dirty water...
another watery keg beer...pretty gross stuff...there isnt much more to say.
is there really any difference between this and regular budweiser?  tastes the same to me.
im not quite sure what the point of commenting on this beer is...i think every human being on the planet has tried it.
I also agree with aarossell, although his rating is awfully generous...this stuff is nasty
I agree with Anglofile.  This is barely suitable for human consumption...pretty nasty stuff...
This is a perfect beer for those who are poor, drink a lot, but cant stomach the typical piss-tasting keg beers.
